Moustapha Abdoulaye Hima (amụrụ ya na 1 Jenụwarị 1992) bụ onye na-akụ ọkpọ na Nijeria
O sonyere Niger na  Summer Olympics nke afọ 2012 dị ka onye na-agba ti ọkpọ (69 kilogram)

Abdoulaye Hima bụ onye na-eburu ọkọlọtọ Niger n'ememe mmeghe. N'abalị iri abụọ na itoolu n'ọnwa Julaị, Abdoulaye Hima meriri Cameron Hammond nke Australia site na mkpebi 6-13 na agba nke iri atọ na abụọ.
